msgid "...This door doesn't seem to open."
msgstr "...这扇门看起来打不开。"

msgid "So I AM trapped here after all, just not in that tiny cell."
msgstr "所以我还是被困在这里了，只是不在那个小牢房里罢了。"

msgid "I suppose that's less bad..."
msgstr "我想这还不算太坏吧..."

msgid "Alright, vent it is."
msgstr "好吧，去看看通风口吧。"

msgid "Let's hope there's another way out."
msgstr "希望这里还有其他出口吧。"

msgid "The door won't open."
msgstr "门打不开。"

msgid "Looks like human bones."
msgstr "看起来像是人类的骨头。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Dungeon_1.misc_cell_1.dlg.narrator"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "It doesn't open. Something seems to be holding it from the other side."
msgstr "打不开。似乎有什么东西从另一边顶住了。"

msgid "\"Subject 66. Age: 38. Sex: Female. Status: Incapacitated. Extraction scheduled. Priority: Medium.\""
msgstr "“实验体66号。年龄：38。性别：女性。状态：丧失行为能力。已提取计划。优先级：中等。”"

msgid "That's not me. Someone else must've been kept in here."
msgstr "这不是我吧。之前一定有人被关在这里。"

msgid "It was just... open?"
msgstr "这就...打开了？"

msgid "\"Subject 41. Age: 53. Sex: Male. Status: Incapacitated. Extraction scheduled. Priority: Low.\""
msgstr "“实验体41号。年龄：53。性别：男性。状态：丧失行为能力。已提取计划。优先级：低。”"

msgid "\"Subject 37. Age: 13. Sex: Male. Status: Incapacitated. Extraction on hold. Awaiting further results. Follow-up tests scheduled. Priority: High.\""
msgstr "“实验体37号。年龄：13。性别：男性。状态：丧失行为能力。正在提取。正在等待进一步结果。已安排后续测试。优先级：高。”"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Dungeon_1.misc_cell_5.dlg.narrator"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "It doesn't open anymore. Something seems to be holding it from the other side."
msgstr "打不开了。似乎有什么东西从另一侧顶住了。"

msgid "These are my things... most of it anyway."
msgstr "这些是我的东西...总之大部分是。"

msgid "I hadn't even noticed I had lost them."
msgstr "我甚至都没注意到我把它们弄丢了。"

msgid "Why are they here...?"
msgstr "为什么它们会在这里呢...？"

msgid "(You got your items back.)"
msgstr "（你把你的物品拿了回来。）"

msgid "There's nothing else on the desk."
msgstr "桌子上没有其他东西了。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Dungeon_1.misc_desk_left.dlg.narrator"
msgid "The drawers are empty."
msgstr "抽屉是空的。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Dungeon_1.misc_desk_right.dlg.narrator"
msgid "The drawers are empty."
msgstr "抽屉是空的。"

msgid "A huge hole."
msgstr "一个大洞。"

msgid "I hope the floor is stable..."
msgstr "我希望地板还是稳定的..."

msgid "This vent is suspicious."
msgstr "这个通风口很可疑。"

msgid "Maybe I could escape through here?"
msgstr "也许我能从这里逃出去？"

msgid "It's almost like it's inviting me in."
msgstr "它看起来就像在欢迎我进去一样。"

msgid "It's too high to reach."
msgstr "太高了，够不到。"

msgid "Wait, there's something on the desk."
msgstr "等等，桌上有东西。"

msgid "Climb the box and remove the vent cover?"
msgstr "要爬上箱子，取下通风口盖吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Dungeon_1.move_climb.choice.Climb the box and remove the vent cover?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Dungeon_1.move_climb.choice.Climb the box and remove the vent cover?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "Crawl into the vents?"
msgstr "要爬进通风口吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Dungeon_1.move_climb.choice.Crawl into the vents?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Dungeon_1.move_climb.choice.Crawl into the vents?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "No... at that point, it would just be silly."
msgstr "不...已经到这种地步了，那样的话就太傻了。"

msgid "That guy is waiting for me outside..."
msgstr "那个家伙还在外面等着我..."

msgid "If I go through here right now, it would take him a while to realize I left."
msgstr "如果我现在过去，他要过一段时间才会意识到我离开了。"

msgid "I could get rid of him that way, I think."
msgstr "我想，这样我就能摆脱他了。"

msgid "Go through the vent and leave Sai behind?"
msgstr "要从通风口出去，丢下赛伊吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Dungeon_1.move_climb.choice.Go through the vent and leave Sai behind?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Dungeon_1.move_climb.choice.Go through the vent and leave Sai behind?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "No... that would probably be pretty rude."
msgstr "不...这样也太不礼貌了。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B2F_Dungeon_1.move_climb.dlg.lacie"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "Having fun?"
msgstr "好玩吗？"

msgid "...Yep, plenty."
msgstr "...对，蛮好玩的。"

msgid "Let's go then?"
msgstr "那我们走吧？"

msgid "Safe!"
msgstr "安全了！"

msgid "(Sai joined your party.)"
msgstr "（赛伊加入了你的队伍。）"
